panels.name: Event Names by User Agent
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$Cloudtrail "apigateway.amazonaws.com"
| json field=_raw "userAgent" nodrop
| json field=_raw "awsRegion"
| json field=_raw "eventSource" nodrop
| json field=_raw "eventName" nodrop
| json field=_raw "requestParameters.basePath" as basePath nodrop
| json field=_raw "requestParameters.domainName" as domainName nodrop
| where eventSource = "apigateway.amazonaws.com"
| timeslice 1h
| count by eventName, userAgent
| transpose row eventName column userAgent
